resources.string:
Le app lena yeku kala kuvimbeleka ne kugcindzetela kusebentisa kwemubane wetekuchuma.

ngabe likhasi lemoya lelinemininingwane kanye netekuchumana emoyeni tivinjiwe yini? ngabe umbane wemoya uhamba kancane ngendlela lecakile yini? 

 Vula OONI Probe kutokwati kabanti!
Imininingwane ya OONI isakateka ngalokusebaleni futsi itofaka ekhatsi imininingwane yakho yetekuchumana emoyeni.
Noma ngabe ngubani lolandzelela tindlela takho tekuchumana emoyeni (kungaba ngu hulumende noma labaphetse tona tekuchumana emoyeni eveni lakho) batawubona kutsi wena usebentisa OONI Probe.
Ungawahlola emakhasi emoya lanemininingwane lavinjiwe (kepha ungakhetsa kutsi ngumaphi lamakhasi lofuna kuwahlola).
Uma ngabe ukhona lolandzelela kusebenta kwembane wami wetekuchumana, utawubona kutsi ngisebentisa OONI Probe.

OONI Probe akasilo lithulusi langansense noma leliyimfihlo. Noma ngubani lolandzelela kusebenta kwetindlela takho tekuchumana emoyeni utawukhona kubona kutsi usebentisa luphi luhlobo lwetebucwephesha.
Ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi uma ngisebentisa OONI Probe, imininingwane yetekuchumana lengiyikolekako itawuvele isakateke ngephandle kwekuvuma nome kuphika kwami.
